    <body>
      <div type="page" n="164">
        <pb n="164"/>
        <lg xml:id="block_A" xml:lang="he" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F9e003d6e-2f94-40ff-b17f-44c953d93d85.jp2/1637,773,1290,1032/max/0/default.jpg">
          <l>תְּפִלָּה</l>
          <l>T FILAH</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="block_B" xml:lang="he" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F9e003d6e-2f94-40ff-b17f-44c953d93d85.jp2/2808,2282,1379,446/max/0/default.jpg">
          <l>אֲדֹנָי, שְׂפָתַי תִּפְתָּח,</l>
          <l>וּפִי יַגִיד תְּהִלָּתֶךָ.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="block_C" xml:lang="en" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F9e003d6e-2f94-40ff-b17f-44c953d93d85.jp2/416,2232,2859,1181/max/0/default.jpg">
          <l>ADONAI, s&apos;fatai tiftach,</l>
          <l>ufi yagid t&apos;hilatecha.</l>
          <l>ADONAI, open up my lips,</l>
          <l>that my mouth may declare Your praise.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="block_D" xml:lang="en" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F9e003d6e-2f94-40ff-b17f-44c953d93d85.jp2/422,5736,3350,600/max/0/default.jpg">
          <l>For those who choose: Before reciting T&apos;filah, one takes three</l>
          <l>steps forward.</l>
          <l>Adonai, sfatai tiftach... Adonai, open up my lips... Psalm 51:17</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
